common.profile_tab_limit_msg:
The newest pages that users viewed are saved in computer memory temporarily. Therefore, the number of pages that users set in Tab Limit is displayed quickly when users move to other menus.
If computer has low specification, the speed may be slow.
So make sure that Tab limit should be set small number.

Ex)If users set Tab Limit is '3', move to Mail>Board>Task and go back to Mail.
The same page is opened in mail will be displayed again because it is saved in computer memory.
Move to Mail>Board>Task>Circular and go back to Mail, the page is set as [ Start Screen] in Mail will be displayed from server.
The newest 3 menus that Board, Task, Circular are saved in memory except Mail.
And Mail brings data from server that's why Mail can't be displayed latest page anymore.

* More Alias Account Information
Alias accounts will distribute emails received from its mail account to another account in the same domain.
For example, if you want to distribute customer support tickets to all your CS staff at the same time,
and all staff use different accounts but the same domain, you can add all their accounts to a single alias account.
admin.mailadmin_aliasuseraddmsg3:

Emails received by 'webmaster@aaa.com' will be sent to selected existing accounts within the same domain.
In this case, you would enter 'webmaster' in the Alias Account field and the actual recipient accounts in the Existing Accounts field.
